comments: Morant (MEM) briefly places his forearm to Beverley's (LAC) side and marginal contact occurs during his shot attempt near the rim.
Clarke (MEM) touched the ball after it was out of the imaginary cylinder above the rim.
Edwards (MIN) maintains a legal guarding position on Morant (MEM) during the drive.
Vanderbilt (MIN) jumps from point A to point B and makes contact with Clarke (MEM) that affects his shot attempt near the rim.
Towns (MIN) establishes himself in a legal position in Bane's (MEM) path and he is firming up when the marginal contact occurs during the pick.
Konchar (MEM) makes contact to the body of Edwards (MIN) at the end of the drive and the contact affects is SQBR.
Bane (MEM) slightly extends his forearm and it makes contact to Russell's (MIN) arm as he drives towards the rim. Russell's momentum carries him away from the marginal contact.
Beverley (MIN) and Morant (MEM) mutually engage in marginal contact prior to separating during the made shot attempt.
Following Bane's (MEM) made shot attempt, Beverley (MIN) and Morant (MEM) mutually engage in marginal contact prior to separating.
Towns (MIN) establishes himself in a screening position in Morant's (MEM) path and does not deliver contact.
Towns (MIN) abruptly extends his leg into Clarke (MEM) following the jump shot attempt and the contact affects Clarke's ability to land safely.
Clarke (MEM) establishes himself in a screening position in Beverley's (MIN) path and makes marginal contact as they disengage.
Konchar (MEM) momentarily places his arm to Towns' (MIN) body and slides his hand off as they separate.
Morant (MEM) lightly brushes Beverley's (MIN) arm and the marginal contact does not affect his ability to gather the all.
Russell (MIN) and Morant (MEM) mutually engage and disengage with one another prior to the inbound pass.
Towns (MIN) extends his forearm into Jackson Jr.'s (MEM) back and he initiates contact that affects Jackson Jr.'s ability to defend the oncoming driving shot attempt.
Beverley (MIN) briefly places his hand on Morant's (MEM) body during his dribble and then disengages from the marginal contact.
Edwards (MIN) makes marginal contact with Clarke (MEM) as they pursue the loose ball.
Russell (MIN) commits a take foul on Bane (MEM).
Edwards (MIN) dislodges the ball from Morant (MEM) as he attempts to gather the loose ball before incidental contact occurs.
Edwards (MIN) commits a take foul on Morant (MEM).
